I"ü<p><a href="https://modelo.io/">Modelo</a> is a no-frills 3D model, PDF, and image communication and markup tool. It can be used to upload Rhino, Revit and Sketchup models for the purpose of design review and discussion.</p>

<p><img src="../img/software/modelo_demo.jpg" alt="Modelo Demo" title="Modelo Demo" /></p>

<hr />

<p><strong>Features and Tips</strong>
<img src="../img/software/features.png" alt="alt text" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>Mobile VR capable (Google Cardboard, Samsung Gear).</li>
  <li>Modelo has limited rendering and texture mapping capabilitiesâ€”but thatâ€™s kind of the idea.</li>
  <li>It is great for creating simple walk throughs and interactive presentations, and could potentially be used for a design crit.</li>
  <li>Great tool for handling mixed media in a single project repository.</li>
  <li>Multiple folders can be created in each project repository to simulate different phases of the project.</li>
</ul>

